import sys
lines = list(map(str.strip, sys.stdin.readlines()))
for line in lines[2::2]:
    nums = list(map(int, line.split(' ')))
    nums.sort()
    bad = False
    for i in range(len(nums) - 1):
        if nums[i] >= nums[i + 1]:
            bad = True
            break
    print('NO' if bad else 'YES')
